<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.1.8">
<l>kaṟaiyār neṭuvēl maṟamaṉṉar vīya vicayaṉ tērkaṭavi</l>
<l>yiṟaiyāṉ kaiyil niṟaiyāta muṇṭam niṟaitta ventaiyiṭam</l>
<l>maṟaiyāl mūttī yavaivaḷarkkum maṉṉu pukaḻāl vaṇmaiyāl</l>
<l>poṟaiyāl mikka vantaṇarvāḻ puḷḷam pūtaṅ kuṭitāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of our father who, having driven Vijaya’s chariot</l>
<l rend="indent">so that powerful kings with long, blood-covered spears perished,</l>
<l>Filled the unfillable skull in the hand of the god,</l>
<l>Is Puḷḷampūtankuṭi where dwell priests who are superior</l>
<l rend="indent">due to [their] knowledge of the Vedas,</l>
<l>To their eternal renown in nurturing the three fires, to their altruism,</l>
<l rend="indent">and to their forbearance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
